Exit emulatior
.IP "\fBCtrl-a s\fR" 4
.IX Item "Ctrl-a s"
Save disk data back to file (if \-snapshot)
.IP "\fBCtrl-a b\fR" 4
.IX Item "Ctrl-a b"
Send break (magic sysrq in Linux)
.IP "\fBCtrl-a c\fR" 4
.IX Item "Ctrl-a c"
Switch between console and monitor
.IP "\fBCtrl-a Ctrl-a\fR" 4
.IX Item "Ctrl-a Ctrl-a"
Send Ctrl-a
.PP
